Date Reviewed: 01/09/07 nick.gowlett Member Since: 15/08/07
View Member's: Reviews Ordering online didn't work via the Paypal route. Item was said to be in stock, delivery in 5 days. After 8 days I emailed Rebelio and learned it would be despatched in a further week. My card payment was debited the day I made the order! The item when received was foreign mdel with 2-pin power supply. Luckily I notified Rebelio just within their 48 hour limit which I think unreasonable. Now waiting for their reply. What a waste of time! Overall Rating
Date Reviewed: 31/08/07 sarah.oliver1207 Member Since: 22/08/07
View Member's: Reviews The cheapest by far with 2 year warranty and finance - I now change this to an absolute shambles - ordered on Wednesday it took 8 days for them to tell me that they had mucked up my order financially and they cancelled it. I had quite a few conversations with the Chat services and emails and they were cotradicting each other and quite unhelpful. I wasted a lot of time and got nothing out of it. Retailer Response (05/09/07): The customer decided to amend his address after a contract had already been signed and completed with V12 finance. As soon as this request came to Rebelio we passed it on, V12 finance had advised we would need to finally cancel the order and the customer would need to make a new application with the new modified address. Overall Rating

Date Reviewed: 20/05/07 chrismac1812 Member Since: 26/10/05
View Member's: Reviews First time user. Not a positive experience. Payment was taken the day after I ordered. No email to say there was a delay relating to "stock" being unavailable. Despite two emails from me, an initial error (mine) relating to the address meant a further delay in delivery. 18 days after the initial order was placed the goods finally arrived and I think I might have still been waiting if I had not repeatedly emailed and finally cancelled part of the order. I am still waiting for a partial refund. I am unlikely to be a returning customer. I use Ebay regularly and this is the worst feedback I have ever left for any internet based company! Overall Rating

View Member's: Reviews I was told the item was in stock and next day delivery. After a couple of days i chased them to be told there was an error, none in stock. Chased again after a few days, still no stock then found out that they had billed me right from the beginning. So they have had my money for over a week - have no idea when they will have stock- and i have done all the chasing. Despite what others say in eight years of Internet shopping worst experinece to date bar none. Overall Rating
